title: PHOTO GALLERY: Daniel Murphy's 7 postseason home runs
text: > Top News PHOTO GALLERY: Daniel Murphy's 7 postseason home runs FILE - On top, in this Oct. 18, 2015, file photo, New York Mets' Daniel Murphy hits his fifth 2015 postseason home run, during the first inning of Game 2 of the National League baseball championship series against the Chicago Cubs in New York. Below, also in an Oct. 18, 2015, file photo, Mets' Daniel Murphy celebrates after hitting the two-run home run during the first inning of Game 2 of the National League baseball championship series against the Cubs in New York. Murphy won NL Championship Series MVP on Wednesday night, Oct. 21, 2015, after homering for a postseason-record sixth straight game, leading the Mets over the Chicago Cubs 8-3 to complete a four-game sweep. (AP Photo/File)
